<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Error al Confirmar</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8d7da;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .card {
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .error-icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: #dc3545;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card text-center p-4">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <i class="bi bi-x-circle-fill error-icon"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h2 class="text-danger">¡Ha ocurrido un error!</h2>
                        <p class="text-muted">No se pudo confirmar su solicitud. Comuníquese con su administrador de sistemas.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
